Question: Davolink Co., Ltd CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Davolink Co., Ltd

CES 2024

- Introducing the latest high-speed wireless router
- 10 gigabit ports for ultra-fast wired connections
- Next-generation Wi-Fi 6E technology for enhanced wireless performance
- Multi-user MIMO technology for improved simultaneous data transfer
- Advanced security features including WPA3 encryption and parental controls
